{"tid":1679425,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「吃上帝的飯，辦習帝的事」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-28T08:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:06:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7097c5fbf0b122849bbc5ef92f2cadb3dfa0aaf","tid":1679425,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191028/20794978/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20794978%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD50lZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=88f64190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20794978%2F&h=0112f378\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191028/20794978/</a><br />\n<br />\n「吃上帝的飯，辦習帝的事」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191028/large/1572160793_6fe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572160793_6fe0.jpg&h=eb37b455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都明白，現今還有人打死一份工嗎？馬太福音告誡一個人不能事奉兩個主，你們不能「既事奉上帝，又事奉瑪門（權勢財利）」。中國人早就參透了，歇後語曰：「吃曹操的飯，辦劉備的事」，並非吃裏扒外，只是多份「兼職」而已。<br />\n<br />\n──所以「吃上帝的飯，辦習帝的事」一點也不奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳被剛愎自用愚蠢低能的林鄭，利用為送中惡法掩飾藉口，搞到法治經濟淪喪，死傷無數，借一命害百命，政警鄉黑勾結砸爛香港，還企圖以宗教助力化解困局，大罪魁禍首把小罪魁禍首丟到台灣去處置？人家總統大選得你助攻谷底反彈，一切當然政治化，陰毒蛾鬥不過麻辣英。人蠢冇藥醫，喪心變喪屍，惟有靠牧師。<br />\n<br />\n這聖公會教省秘書長，身兼北京市政協委員的管浩鳴牧師（簡稱「管紅牧」），向以舔共見著。他對只能因洗黑錢坐牢廿多月逃過殺人案件審判的陳同佳甚為熱心，擔起中間人特務，但管太多了，像國產零零漆，看來是個按摩機實際上是架吸塵機之類，身兼代言人、政客、殺手經理人、社工、政府漂白師、安家費斡旋者、伴遊、收<br />\n𡃁養鬼仔、監護人&hellip;&hellip;油滑張揚，超越「神職人員」本份，被台方陸委會主席譏諷「若有心為女死者伸張正義少講兩句話」。才不！少管閑事怎再上層樓？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f134f2c7cb1b718189df83154d5324601cc3e191","tid":1679425,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c502a88d1f78a66178bdb00b9fed3892124adb0","tid":1679425,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f35705958b0bc98114b4c9574fd338706dde3ac","tid":1679425,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10月31星期四：太子靈堂悼念太子站事件兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11月2星期六：維園集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ayU5dBt.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/wQNKuag.jpg\" />"}]}